                            | Third Party Applications/Websites. 
                        | Massie has no control over the privacy practices of websites or applications that she do not own.
                    li
                        strong
                            | Changes To This Privacy Policy. 
                        | Massie may change this privacy policy and practices over time. To the extent that this policy changes in a material way, the policy that was in place at the time that you submitted personal information to Massie will generally govern that information unless she receives your consent to the new privacy policy. 
            .point
